Our President often carries out various unexpected daring and bold operations. For example, in 2012, during the presidential elections in the Russian Federation, he performed a brilliant plastic surgery on his face. Do you know why? Because according to the Constitution of the Russian Federation, "the same person cannot occupy position of the President of the Russian Federation for more than two terms. "And Putin very strictly observes the Constitution. So in 2024, after the expiration of the next two terms, we can expect a new (updated) face to appear in him, even better and more beautiful